      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Laguna Seca Blue. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the Double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been structurally reinforced. Power is delivered to the tarmac via a factory M-variable differential lock. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a factory-fresh interior, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
